.css-jfmysa{display:inline;word-break:break-word;} .css-1ankfgb{cursor:pointer;display:inline;word-break:break-word;} Nepal has ordered private schools to stop double-charging fees, repay illegally collected ones and clearly publish their pricing structures, reopening a debate about education costs that runs across South Asia.

